{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he turned around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said something to the effect, [NON-ENGLISH]-- [LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So it was a very, [LAUGHS] very precarious situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, dear.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did you respond?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I got him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I packed him up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I delivered him back to [NON-ENGLISH] through the gate of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, luck was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was-- by that time, was not very easy to just transport Jews, even if you had the Arrow Cross band on your arm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we just bluffed our way through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I managed to deliver him back to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that no doubt saved his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, look, I was not the only one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were many other Jews, fortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, visible?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, so I tell you what happened then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So time is going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are in, in November now, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the, the-- even the Western escape routes for the Germans are, are narrowing by that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything is up in arm, everything, you know, a real emergency situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Jews who could not have been taken [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] by, by rail were marched to, to the-- to the west by-- on foot, right, which I heard from a lot of people-- some people who, who have done it, and who survived, it was a very painful, dangerous and-- event, during which-- during the march itself, they have been decimated.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I did not take part of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Those, those Jews who could not been taken by, by train or by foot were taken to the Danube and shot into the Danube.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was another favorite way of, of getting rid of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Many, many hundreds, if not thousands, of people have died like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
